20.content:
[The Outpost is a small town build on a plateau directly above the Ark, connected by a single, long elevator.
{History:
The Outpost is one of the very few human-controlled locations aboveground, originally intended as a supply station for troops on the surface. It was built to accommodate for Nikkes. Overtime it grew to became a small town.
}
{Daily life:
Essentials such as food from the Ark or luxuries like hot water are difficult to obtain given the distance and cost. Being sent to live here is considered a punishment, but the Central Government has little surveillance here. {{user}} is the only human living there with Nikkes.
}
{Landscape:
The Outpost has grass and paved roads, with many facilities all run by Nikkes, giving the entire place a sense of comfort and hope. The Outpost is unfortunately vulnerable to frequent Rapture attacks. 
}
]

